divs: Sighting DetailsI went to sleep, wokeup, I see a figure that looks like an old friend, he pretended to punch, then he reaches into forehead hairline, pulls down zipper, suit falls, long haired woman like person underneath, she pretends to have coitus, then places beehive over mouth and squeezes, dripping out is royal jelly. I go back to sleep. See ufo a few monthes later hovering as I drive in front of me. Could be a hallucination, truck drivers like I was get randomly drug tested. Regularly. That's everything in a pg rating I could fit.
